Build a Recipe Class:

XXX A recipe has a name
XXX A recipe has a description
XXX Recipe#name returns the name of the recipe
XXX Recipe#description returns the description for the recipe
XXX The name of the recipe cannot be changed
XXX The description of the recipe can be updated
XXX Recipe.all returns a list of all of the recipes that have been created


Build a Restaurant Class:
XXX A restaurant has a name
XXX A restaurant has a star_rating which is an integer
XXX A restaurant can change its name and its star_rating


